How to start door handle detection

1) launch pico flexx camera: roslaunch pico_flexx_driver pico_flexx_driver.launch publish_tf:=true base_name_tf:=pico_flexx_optical_frame
2) record rosbag file of the door handle: rosbag record -a --duration=30
3) disconnect pico flexx camera
4) play rosbag file in a loop: rosbag play -l test.bag
5) visualize rosbag in rviz: 
fixed frame: pico_flexx_optical_frame_optical_frame
topic: /pico_flexx/points

6) cd git/care-o-bot-indigo/
7) start detection node: rosrun ipa_door_handle_detection ipa_door_handle_detection_TM
8) See segmented door handle select:
 fixed_frame: pico_flexx_optical_frame
 topic: /door_handle
 select color in Color Transformer to view doorhandle in red and door plane in green

9) Add coordinate system of the detected door handle: 
Add Axes with reference frame: cluster_KOS
